22:39.624 --> 22:41.126
♪♪ Oh, my ♪♪

22:41.626 --> 22:43.128
♪♪ And maybe I seem
a bit confused ♪♪

22:43.628 --> 22:45.931
♪♪ Well, maybe,
but I got you pegged ♪♪

22:45.931 --> 22:48.100
(laughs)

22:48.100 --> 22:50.102
♪♪ But I don'’’t know what to do
 ♪♪

